onprofessioneel, <delay8 />hè?<delay40 /> <anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Nou, ahum<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="021_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Leuk je te leren kennen!<delay20 /> <anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ik ben
